=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">一些WC任務的翻譯</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">最近找到一些任務，我試著把一些翻出來，給大伙參考，有些地方不是很好，請大多多包含，有錯的地方也請指正，謝謝。註：我有把英文原文放上，再把我的翻譯放在下方，如有先進覺得不好，也請修正，謝謝。 <BR>  <BR> Western Commonlands <BR> Mission one Armor size:  There are two dwarven smiths at the inn next to Befallen who offer to resize Crafted Armor for you.  This reduces the size to small and the weight of the armor as follows:  Gauntlets were 5.0 now 3.7 wt. Vambraces were 6.5 now 4.8 wt. Bracers were 4.0 now 3.0 wt each. Helm was 6.0 now 4.5 wt. Pauldron was 4.5 now 3.3 wt. Breastplate was 10.0 now 7.5 wt. Greaves were 7.5 now 5.6 wt. Plate boots were 6.5 now 4.8 wt.  <BR> 任務1 盔甲尺寸：在Befallen附近的旅館那有兩個提供更改尺寸的Crafted Armor給你的Dwarven Smiths。減小其尺寸到小型和重量如下：鐵手套(Gauntlets)現在是5.0 改成3.7wt。Vambraces 目前是6.5改成4.8wt。臂鐲(Bracers)現在是4.0 改成每個3.0 wt。頭盔(Helm)現在是6.0改成4.5wt。Pauldron現在是4.5放成3.3 wt。胸甲(Breastplate)現在是10.0改成7.5wt。脛甲(Greaves)現在是7.5改成5.6wt。鐵鞋(Plate boots)現在是6.5改成4.8wt。 <BR>  <BR> Mission two Noresa's Purse:  This quest description is found in the Rogue Redemption Quest in Solusek Ro.  <BR> 任務2Noresa的願望：這個記載在Solusek Ro的Rogue Redemption 任務中被發現。(這個只有這樣，只做參考，目前還沒找到解法) <BR>  <BR> Mission three Paladin Message:  Theron Rolius, in the Hall of Truth, standing next to the paladin guildmaster in the rear raised section, is the person who initiates this quest. He asks you to meet a messenger named Mojax Hikspin &quot;near a lake in the Commonlands&quot;.  When found in West Commonlands, he is usually sitting next to the fisherman on the lake - the one that won't talk or sell to you.  He needs a flask of milk, which you can get from the office of the people or at Greenleaf's in Freeport.  As soon as you give him the milk, he starts to hand you a note, but a fast NPC named Duggin Scumper comes by, insults the Freeport king or something, and runs off, yelling that You'll never catch him, and that he's taking this to his superior in the Quenos Royal hall or something.  In order to get the note, you have to attack the man, kill him (he's around level 3 or 4) and loot his corpse to find the note.  Then you return the note to Eeyana Neastra, a sentry on the top level of the temple of Marr (she may be in the Hall of Truth now).  He is very tough to catch without magic.   However, sometimes if you stop chasing him and return to Mojax, he will walk down the path to a pillar and drop the note for you there.  Each time you give Mojax milk, you restart the sequence so that you can try again if you mis the first time.  You get a little gold, a item (sometimes a potion), experience, and increased faction standing with the Knights of Truth.  (Submitted by Saidan)  <BR> 任務3 聖騎士的訊息：Theron Rolius ，在真實之堡，就站在建築物後方聖騎士公會導師的附近，就是會你這個任務的人。他要求你去和一個叫Mojax Hikspin 的傳訊人見面，就在Commonland的湖附近(near a lake in the commonland)。當在West commonland 發現時，他通常坐在那個在湖旁不會和你說話和賣東西給你的釣魚者旁邊。他需要一瓶你可以在Freeport 的人民辦事處(the office of the people)或Greenleaf’s買到的牛奶。儘可能快速的給他牛奶，他開始傳遞這筆記給你，但是一個快速的NPC叫Duggin Scumper的經過，侮辱Freeport的國王或某事，並且跑走，大叫說你將永遠捉不到他和他正帶走這給他在Quenos國家宮殿的高手或什麼事。為了要得到這筆記，你必需攻擊這男人，殺了他(他大約在Lv3到Lv4)，撿他的屍體去找到這筆記。接著你把這筆記交回給Eeyana Neastra一個Marr之宮殿的高級等守衛(她現在大概在真實宮殿)。他是非常困難去捉到在沒有施法的狀況下。但是，有時如果你停止追他並走回Mojax，他將走下到紀念碑的道路並丟下這筆記到你那。每次你給Mojox牛奶，你就重新開始這個任務，所以如果你錯過了第一次，你可以再試一次。你得到一點黃金，一個物品(有時是一瓶藥水)，經驗值和增加你對Knights of Truth的faction(由Submitted提供)。 <BR>  <BR> Mission four Reserve Militia:  Talk to Armorer Delin in the Freeport Militia House and he will ask you to show him your reserve militia token.  If you don't have one, he tells you to go talk to Guard Valorn out at  the tollbooth in West Commonlands.  Valorn gives out the 4 orc picks quest then will give you the bracketed  keyword for the next quest.  Which is to bring 8 cutthroat rings combined in a bag he gives you.  Give him that and he gives you a reserve militia tolken, which when you give that to Armorer Delin in the militia house results in a Reserve Militia Tunic.  After giving you the tunic, the Armorer tells you to be careful of north freeport.  Coalition of TradefolkIII, and Freeport Militia go up.  Knighhts of Truth and Mithaniel Marr go down.  <BR> 任務4 預備的民兵：和Freeport民兵所的Armorer Delin說話，他將要求你出示你的預備民是錢幣。如果你沒有，他告訴你去和遠在West Commonlands 哨所的Guard Valorn說話。Valorn 發給你 找尋4 Orc 的任務，接著給你下一個任務的相關關鍵。他給你一個你必需裝8 個Cutthroat rings 的袋子。給他這個袋子，他會給你一個預備民兵錢幣，就是你要把這給在民兵所的Armorer Delin而換得預備民兵服。在給你這個服裝後，Armorer 告訴你要小心北Freeport。你對Coalition of TradefolkIII 和 Freeport Militia 的faction將會上升。Knights of Truth 和Mithaniel Marr 的faction 下降。 <BR>   <BR>  <BR> </font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR></TABLE></TD></TR></TABLE>